00:39:08.176 --> 00:39:11.716
levels, assuming that I knew what they were, and we have

641
00:39:11.776 --> 00:39:14.836
the clinician here at 25% on dose level three.

642
00:39:15.436 --> 00:39:19.115
And if the patient is also 35%, then it's not of concern. Right?

643
00:39:19.216 --> 00:39:23.136
If I use my standard method, I would be recommending any

644
00:39:23.156 --> 00:39:24.016
doses below

