00:41:47.536 --> 00:41:48.596
a dose

687
00:41:50.216 --> 00:41:50.946
assignment component.

688
00:41:52.466 --> 00:41:56.356
The PRO CRM has also been applied in practice in a phase one study

689
00:41:56.436 --> 00:41:59.756
of radiation therapy. This is as an

690
00:41:59.796 --> 00:42:02.606
example of how they chose the thresholds.

